  classroom(id: $id) {
    
  id
  tzData {
    
  timeZone
  tzOffset
  tzLongName
  tzShortName

  }
  state
  age
  activities: interests

    teacher {
      
  id
  name
  email
  admin
  chatIdentity
  newsletterEnabled
  nickname
  emailVerified
  locale
  phoneNumber
  location {
   
latitude,
longitude,
name

  }

    }
    availabilities {
      
  day
  startTime
  duration

    }
    activeEmpaticoClass {
      
  id
  chatKey
  videoKey
  planningVideoKey
  state

      calendarEvent {
        
  id
  startTime
  endTime
  activity
  state

        sender {
          
  id
  name
  email
  admin
  chatIdentity
  newsletterEnabled
  nickname
  emailVerified
  locale
  phoneNumber
  location {
   
latitude,
longitude,
name

  }

        }
        canceler {
          
  id
  name
  email
  admin
  chatIdentity
  newsletterEnabled
  nickname
  emailVerified
  locale
  phoneNumber
  location {
   
latitude,
longitude,
name

  }

        }
      }
      partnerClassroom(not: $id) {
        
  id
  tzData {
    
  timeZone
  tzOffset
  tzLongName
  tzShortName

  }
  state
  age
  activities: interests

        availabilities {
          
  day
  startTime
  duration

        }
        teacher {
          
  id
  name
  email
  admin
  chatIdentity
  newsletterEnabled
  nickname
  emailVerified
  locale
  phoneNumber
  location {
   
latitude,
longitude,
name

  }

        }
      }
    }
  }
}
